## App Modules

### Shopper App
@features
- Supabase Auth (OTP, email/phone)
- Profile & Bank/UPI linking
- Campaign Discovery + Filtering
- Enroll, Submit Deliverables
- Payout Progress UI: Pending → Paid
- Alert System: Push, Email, WhatsApp
- Edit Profile + Preferences

### Brand App
@features
- Brand KYC Verification
- Create/Manage Campaigns
- View Submissions + Approve/Reject
- Invoice & Payment Management
- Admin Team Roles
- Alert System (same as above)

### Admin App
@features
- Superuser Dashboard
- User/Campaign/Payout/Dispute Moderation
- Invoice Monitoring
- Campaign Audit & Logs
- Coupon Management

---

## Automated Logic

- Inactive Campaigns auto-expire in 14 days
- Auto-approve deliverables after 7 days
- Auto-retry failed payouts
- Generate overdue invoice alerts
- Log coupon lifecycle events

