## Build, Deploy, and Store Guidelines

- Use `eas.json` for CI/CD configuration (Dev, Preview, Prod)
- Deploy with `eas build`, `eas submit`
- Setup TestFlight and Google Play testing tracks
- Use `expo-constants` for env vars (API, App IDs)
- Auto versioning via `expo-updates` and git tagging

